text: Georges André Weingand (14 March 1915 - 6 March 2004) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:2004 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics
